quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  20,88,to is ne un ke liye aik bitchrha bana diya ( yani is ka ) Qalib jis ki aawaz gaaye ki si thi. to log kehnay lagey ke yahi tumhara mabood hai aur moose ka bhi mabood hai. magar woh bhool gay hain
  20,89,kiya yeh log nahi dekhte ke woh un ki kisi baat ka jawab nahi deta. aur nah un ke nuqsaan aur naffa ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhta hai
  20,90,aur Haroon ne un se pehlay hi keh diya tha ke logo is se sirf tumhari azmaish ki gayi hai. aur tumhara perwar-digaar to khuda hai to meri pairwi karo aur mera kaha manu
  20,91,woh kehnay lagey ke jab taq moose hamaray paas wapas nah ayen hum to is ki pooja par qaim rahen ge
  20,92,( phir moose ne Haroon se ) kaha ke Haroon jab tum ne un ko dekha tha ke gumraah ho rahay hain to tum ko kis cheez ne roka
  20,93,( yani ) is baat se ke tum mere peechay chalay aao. bhala tum ne mere hukum ke khilaaf ( kyun )kiya ?
  20,94,kehnay lagey ke bhai meri darhhi aur sir ( ke balon ) ko nah pakriyay. mein to is se dara ke aap yeh nah kahin ke tum ne bani Israel mein tafarruqa daal diya aur meri baat ko malhooz nah rakha
  20,95,phir ( samri se ) kehnay lagey ke samri terakiya haal hai ?
  20,96,is ne kaha ke mein ne aisi cheez dekhi jo ouron ne nahi dekhi to mein ne farishtay ke naqsh pa se ( matti ki ) aik muthi bhar li. phir is ko ( bichhre ke Qalib mein ) daal diya aur mujhe mere jee ne ( is kaam ko ) acha bataya
  20,97,( moose ne ) kaha ja tujh ko duniya ki zindagi mein yeh ( saza ) hai ke kehta rahay ke mujh ko haath nah lagana aur tairay liye aik aur wada hai ( yani azaab ka ) jo tujh se tal nah sakay ga aur jis mabood ( ki pooja ) par to ( qaim o ) mutakif tha is ko dekh. hum usay jaladein ge phir is ( ki raakh ) ko urra kar darya mein bekhair den ge
  20,98,tumhara mabood khuda hi hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi. is ka ilm har cheez par muheet hai
